room_title: Escape room "Jail Break Havana" by Key West Room Escape in Key West
room_description: You’ve really done it this time… On a brief visit to Cuba, you got messed up with the wrong crowd. It seems the guard has been called to pick up some other miscreants, so you have 60 minutes to make a run for it! The only problem is... you’re locked in a cell! Search for clues, unlock the cell, and escape the room!
